160	WebQA was built as a role-gated platform with tester, rater, and admin
161	workflows. The present paper analyzes only Rater Bench data collected
162	by the \texttt{rater} cohort, which uses blinded scoring and forced
163	ranking.
164	
165	\begin{figure*}[t]
