169	  Panel A: benchmark construction, server-side blinding, cohort-specific
170	  rubric collection, and rank validation. Panel B: flat export and its
171	  four downstream products, aggregate analysis, a preferred-response
172	  SFT set, chosen/rejected preference pairs, and safety filtering.}
